						<h2>
							Forum improvements, login should stick now
							Sunday, February 15, 2004 - 11:40:42 AM
						</h2>
						<p>
							<P>When you login, it should keep you logged in until you click the logout button, instead of having to login each time.</P>
<P>Forum Features Added:</P>
<UL>
<LI>You can now sort the thread list for a forum by choosing the desired sort in the drop-down-list above the thread list table.&nbsp; The background color of the list is the same background color as your buttons.&nbsp; So if you have a texture for buttons, and didnt set your background color, you should :)</LI>
<LI>You can mark a forum as read by clicking &nbsp;the Mark Forum Read link next to the sort dropdownlist.</LI>
<LI>You can mark all forums read by clicking the Mark All Forums Read link on the forum list</LI>
<LI>The quick reply text-box background color is now transparent (instead of white), and the forecolor (text color) is the same as your Page Text Color that you defined in the color configuration page.</LI></UL>
<P>I think thats it..&nbsp; I might have missed a thing or two.&nbsp; I probably won`t get to the new skins that I wanted to make, I rented Project Gotham Racer II for my Xbox :) Going to be a little busy :)</P>
						</p>
					
						<hr />
					
