							Added new posts icons for forum list
							Saturday, February 14, 2004 - 7:43:45 AM
						</h2>
						<p>
							<P>When you are logged in and are viewing the forum list, for the new forums, you will now see an icon showing if there are new posts in each forum since your last visit.&nbsp; I will probably add a couple more features over the weekend to the forums..&nbsp; Sorting the threadlist is probably next on the list.</P>
<P>I am also going to try to make up some more skins this weekend, fix some DKP issues, and possibly program a way to add raids without&nbsp;a log file.</P>
<P>Thats my goal anyway :)</P>
						</p>
					
