<P>It honestly wont be hard to implement at all.. i just need the time to do it.&nbsp; Of course the forums have to get done before anything.&nbsp; Lots of guilds are&nbsp;using them, as I am adding features and I am getting some good ideas from the various suggestions!&nbsp; I&nbsp;expect to spend some time today on adding some&nbsp;features .. probably a&nbsp;New messages icon on the forum list to show forums with new messages..&nbsp; </P>
