						<h2>
							Forum features added
							Sunday, February 01, 2004 - 10:43:28 AM
						</h2>
						<p>
							<P>I did a little work on the forums:</P>
<UL>
<LI>Fixed problem with sigs that would cause a dumb border for every line, if DIV tags were used</LI>
<LI>If you have any unread private messages, the number of private messages will be displayed in the private messages button up top</LI>
<LI>When viewing a message thread, you can now click on a PM button to send a private message the user</LI>
<LI>Private messages are now sorted by Date in descending order</LI>
<LI>I increased the height of the post editor</LI></UL>
<P>The old forums seem to have some issue with attachements being added to posts..&nbsp; i have no clue what thats all about.&nbsp; The old forums are really getting on my nerves with this, as well as the damn confirmation emails getting filtered by a lot of ISPs..&nbsp; I cant wait to shut that damn forum off (its a memory hog too!)</P>
						</p>
					
