<P>Admins/officers should really like the amount of control you have over the forums now..&nbsp; it`s a lot better.</P>
<P>You can&nbsp;fool get to the forums by going to the /forum/ directory in your site.. so it would be <A href="http://yoursite.guildwizard.com/forums/">http://yoursite.guildwizard.com/forums/</A>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; .. Make sure you are logged in as an admin or officer so you can add forums and use the Admin panels</P>
