<P>Anyway, with regards to GuildWizard and the forums etc.. I am going to do my best to get the forums finished as soon as I can.&nbsp; I want to implement them, make sure they are working, and then guildwizard is going to run as is, with bug fixes my only work.&nbsp; Then, when things slow down with work, I will start on new features.</P>
<P>The feedback I`ve gotten thus far on the new forums have been good.&nbsp; Looks like I am on the right track based on user input. I am hoping to have a usable forum that people can start using for their own guild sites soon.&nbsp; </P>
